<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4755194>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figs 21–34: Lathrobium egens (21–27) and L. bitaleatum (28–34): forebody (21, 29); male sternite VII (22); male sternite VIII (23); aedeagus in lateral (24, 30, 33), ventral (25, 31), and dorsal view (32, 34); female sternite VIII (26); female tergites IX–X (27); habitus (28). Scale bars: 28: 5.0 mm; 21, 29: 1.0 mm; 22–27, 30–34: 0.5 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4755194/files/figure.png" .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4755192>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figs 15–20: Lathrobium guransicum (15–16) and L. latius (17–20): male sternite VII (15, 17); male sternite VIII (16, 18); aedeagus in lateral and in ventral view (19–20). Scale bars: 15–16: 0.5 mm; 17–20: 0.2 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4755192/files/figure.png" .

